Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:02.02,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:05.16,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}High school student Shin'ichi was forced\Nto take a drug that shrunk him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.16,0:00:07.86,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}If the organization learned that Shin'ichi\Nand Conan were the same person,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.66,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}everyone close to me would be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:12.06,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The only one who knows the truth is Dr. Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:15.05,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I hide my identity yet again today,\Nin which there is only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:55.60,Signs,Comment,0,0,0,,Billion yen robbers still at large!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:55.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Robberies, kidnappings, murders...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:58.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,There's just no end to these crimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:02.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's exactly why your detective skills are proving so useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:04.66,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Old man Kogoro gets all the credit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:09.56,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,All done! These are my special\NCriminal Pursuit Glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.36,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,How do I use these?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:13.42,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Try pressing the button on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:17.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:23.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll display the location of this transmitter within a 20-kilometer radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:26.24,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You can keep it here most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:27.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's like a sticker!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:30.92,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:33.82,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,My name is Masami Hirota!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:37.12,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Please! Find my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:38.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:43.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,My father, who works away from home in Tokyo, quit his taxi driver job,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:46.80,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,and he's been missing for a full month now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:49.10,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So that's why you've come to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:54.20,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I took time off from school in Yamagata to come look for him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:57.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the only one I can turn to now, Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Very well. I'll take on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:02.88,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,This is my father, Kenzo Hirota.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:06.25,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He's 5'9" and 48 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:08.79,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What about this cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:12.59,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's my father's cat. Its name is Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:16.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He has three others named Tei, Gou, and Ou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:19.96,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Finding people isn't really my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:24.23,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}But if he had one of these on him,\NI could've found him in no time at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:30.34,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I know! I'll stick it on Ran and test it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:31.83,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:36.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What the heck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.68,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:40.22,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The transmitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:42.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no! I stuck it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:50.56,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,My mother died when I was little, so my father is my only family!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:53.76,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,If anything were to happen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:05.01,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No. Well, not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.54,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I haven't found any leads...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:09.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.78,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.75,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the third time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.32,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Apparently he didn't socialize much with other people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:20.02,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,and he almost never talked about himself,\Naccording to his coworkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:25.53,Radio,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}Goukai Teiou pulls ahead of the pack to earn his 5th G-1 victory in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.62,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it! It's already been a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.73,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Goukai Teiou?{(Heroic Emperor)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:32.24,Flashback,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's my father's cat. Its name is Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:36.67,Flashback,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}He has three others named Tei, Gou, and Ou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:40.44,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kai, Tei, Gou, and Ou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.38,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Rearrange them and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:45.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,"Goukai Teiou"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:45.28,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,—nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.76,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Goukai Teiou truly is invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:53.89,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, that has to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.86,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} loves horse races!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:58.76,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So he named his cats after a famous horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.20,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.57,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.97,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I bet you can find him at the race track!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:05.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:14.88,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow! This is my first time at a race track!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.21,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's hurry and find Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:20.55,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah, right! Like he'd be that easy to find!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.71,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't be mocking us detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:27.26,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:30.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,See! I'm such a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:32.00,Dialogue Top,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:32.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait! He's purposely gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We don't want to scare him away\Nand then lose him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:39.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:42.26,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll follow him back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:52.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:56.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.72,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Good for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:03.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Doesn't something seem different about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.20,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,She's wearing more grown-up clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,and it looks like she has makeup on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.10,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,She hasn't seen her dad in a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:11.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course she'd wear make up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:21.87,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That case was as easy as pie in the hands of Kogoro Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:46.27,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He's dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:49.74,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We found him after he hanged himself last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.78,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:54.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What about his daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:54.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:58.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You know, Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s daughter?\NThe one who came looking for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:02.19,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh? So there was something going after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:04.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Something wasn't right about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.52,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He said he'd pay me a full years'\Nworth of rent all at once
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:09.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,if I let him have an apartment\Nwith no questions asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:12.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Plus all the bills were brand-new and crisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:15.87,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,My guess is if his daughter did come over,\Nthen she's probably dead too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:19.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean? I thought Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} committed suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:23.03,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The police said it was a murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:28.11,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, it was a homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:32.95,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He was hung from the ceiling after he was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:36.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Judging from the large hand marks on the victim's neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:38.46,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,the murderer must have been quite a large man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:40.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What about his daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,These were lying on the floor\Nnear the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:47.90,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,These are Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:52.97,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Her body hasn't turned up yet,\Nbut I'm pretty sure that she's—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:55.64,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on, now. Don't be so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:59.04,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} might've been murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:04.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And she just found her father, too! How horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:06.58,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We still don't know for sure\Nthat she was murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't give up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:12.06,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}But now what? If only we had a clue to go by!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:14.92,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! I accidentally\Nput the transmitter on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.78,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.66,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, kid! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:29.97,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The fact that it's moving means\NMasami{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} might still be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:32.53,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on! Make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:40.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,A pachinko parlor?!\NWhat's Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no, the battery's dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.68,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to find her quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:53.26,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Ain't no kids allowed in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:57.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.41,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The battery's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:06.44,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Why were you gone so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.11,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.08,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What's up with Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.95,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,She's been like that for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:16.05,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,She must really be worried about Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:18.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Something's weird about that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:21.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He's been looking up here this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:27.53,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He's the man who was hanging out\Nby Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:30.53,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Come to think about it,\Nthe killer was a large man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:32.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He killed Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:37.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait right here! I'll go catch him\Nand find out where Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:46.21,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}? What's happened to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.74,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:56.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I caught him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:58.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:01.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What great luck! Who'd have thought the killer would come to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.27,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Killer?! You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:05.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, right! Then who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.36,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm the same as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:08.64,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:11.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a detective too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:17.18,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, I, too, was asked to find Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:19.72,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,By this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:22.19,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:24.19,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm really a detective, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:26.72,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Then why did you run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:29.76,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That young woman came after me, so I instinctually...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:32.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I've always been sort of a coward...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:35.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I wear these sunglasses\Nso people can't make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:37.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Enough of your stupid excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:47.24,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Get serious! Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s life is at stake here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:48.78,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:53.75,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So you were asked to locate\NKenzo Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} as well, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:59.89,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. But there was something\Nstrange about his family...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:03.39,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,This was the man who hired me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:06.93,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He asked me to find his brother\Nwho left Kyushu for Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.93,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He said his brother was his only relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:12.50,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,His only relative?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:15.54,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was supposed to\Nbe Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s only relative!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:20.74,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's weird, too! Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Nfather came here from Yamagata!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,There can't be two Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}s...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:27.08,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,There's one other thing that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:30.39,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard this from the taxi company that Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} worked at.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:33.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Apparently he would drive the same route every single evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:36.59,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,without bothering to pick up any passengers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.73,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And he would do this at breakneck speeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He was just letting off steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.10,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Happens all the time to middle-aged men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:47.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So, who is this client of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:52.81,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Akira Hirota. 28 years old.\NHe's a large man, over 6 feet 3 inches tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.40,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,A large man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.98,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:59.08,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Could he be the large man\Nthe inspector was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:02.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me! Did you tell this man\Nanything about Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.32,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:08.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And then it was after that\Nthat Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:10.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So I wondered if there was any connection...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:13.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it! This man murdered Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:16.90,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And then he took Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:19.54,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Well? How can I contact him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:21.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He contacts me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.89,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So you don't have any clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:24.67,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:26.98,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:31.78,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no mistake! It's the man\NI ran into at the pachinko parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:38.02,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why did the transmitter on\NMasami{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s watch lead me there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:43.33,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}If he really is the killer, and he was\Nwearing Masami{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:45.63,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}...then she's already—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:47.53,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}—been murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:55.36,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry and recharge it, Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:58.99,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop rushing me! Being impatient\Nisn't going to help you any!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:13:01.03,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But if we don't hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:03.03,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, do you remember the\Nrobbery from the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:05.93,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,the one where they stole a billion yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.77,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, the one with the trio of thieves?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:12.61,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,A security guard was killed when\Nhe recklessly tried to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:14.87,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what he got for taking them lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:17.68,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Calm, cool, and collected...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:20.95,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's your style, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.25,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:35.26,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he really in this hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:38.80,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Definitely! I saw him go in\Non my way home from school!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:42.27,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange! The transmitter hasn't moved at all for a while now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.70,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}He didn't take the watch off and escape, did he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:50.44,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, he's staying in Room 802.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.65,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:14:00.21,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Who'd have thought he was really here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.80,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Just when I'm in a hurry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.56,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:20.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Open up! I know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:30.11,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:41.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,This sweet smell... it's potassium cyanide!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:44.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I see. He couldn't live with what\Nhe had done so he killed himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.50,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We should contact the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:51.00,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's Masami{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.30,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}So he did take it from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.31,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Empty duralumin cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:00.78,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:06.05,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Two separate, yet conflicting\Nrequests to find the same person...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:11.02,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kenzo Hirota{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} acting strange\Nand driving the same route everyday...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.69,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}And then these cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:14.03,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:16.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was single?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.56,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah. He didn't have any daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:21.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Plus he was born and raised in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.87,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:26.07,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! I have this case figured out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:30.34,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}These empty cases are the key\Nto unlocking this mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:33.41,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Masami{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}, Kenzo Hirota, and Akira Hirota...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:35.38,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now that we know they're not relatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.92,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}they have no connection whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:40.62,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}But in the context of the other recent incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:43.06,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}the entire mystery comes unraveled!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:47.43,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}They're the three thieves\Nwho stole the one billion in yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:49.06,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Judging from the number of cases here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:51.23,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}they must have been filled\Nwith the stolen money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:55.44,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}If so, then the reason Hirota{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}\Nsped down the same route everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:58.10,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}was to rehearse their getaway!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:02.51,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Their plan succeeded, but he took\Nall the money for himself and ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:04.44,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}He betrayed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:07.21,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Eager to catch Hirota{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10},\Nthe two partners concocted lies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:09.78,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}and sent separate detectives to locate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:13.79,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}And then when he was found, he was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:19.26,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Killed by the large man,\Nwho was then killed in this very room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:22.56,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Killed by the woman who claimed\Nshe was Hirota{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:30.27,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Perhaps she was the mastermind behind these murders!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:31.67,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:33.61,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Her hairstyle and overall\Nappearance were different,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:35.84,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}but her build and the number of suitcases she had weren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.58,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:43.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I found Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:54.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Ran! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:57.20,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, kid! No cutting in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.90,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Our dad's gonna be chopped into pieces\Nand buried alive in the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:02.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,if we don't hurry and save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,G-Go right ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Follow that taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:09.03,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What about the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:15.21,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The reason she seemed different\Nthe second time we saw her
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:16.52,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}was because when we found Hirota{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10},
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:19.69,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}she was in a hurry\Nand hadn't completed her disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:23.19,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}And then Hirota{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s reaction when he saw her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:26.06,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}That wasn't because he was\Nsurprised to see his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.83,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}It was because he was terrified\Nof the partners he betrayed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.36,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}coming to exact revenge on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.89,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it! Why didn't I realize it sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.67,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What now? We lost her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.61,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm 100% certain she entered this harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:43.51,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's definitely somewhere nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.76,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's the money, Masami Hirota?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.76,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Or should I say, Akemi Miyano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.66,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Okita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:04.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The sleeping drug you gave\Nme to put him to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The instant he drank it, he fell to the ground and stopped moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:10.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:13.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What he had in brute strength\Nhe lacked in intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:16.21,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that he\Nwould alert the authorities
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:20.18,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,by throwing all his money\Naround the instant he got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:22.32,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as someone that\Ndangerous remained alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:24.68,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,my own plans would be hindered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:28.18,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You intended to kill everyone\Nfrom the start, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:37.83,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Now hand over the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:41.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It isn't here! It's being held at a certain location.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:46.21,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sick of you using me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:47.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm through with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:50.38,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you honestly think that is an option?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:51.08,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:54.78,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,After I escape overseas, I'll let\Nyou know where the money is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:19:00.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't have that, now. As long as\Nyou're alive, my plan is in jeopardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:05.42,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Once you're dead, all links\Nto me will have vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:09.66,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I can easily find any number of replacements for you and the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:11.96,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Getting my own hands dirty\Ngoes against my principles,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,but it will be the finishing touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:16.67,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,How simple-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:20.44,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Kill me, and you'll never\Nknow where the money is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.81,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I have a pretty good idea where to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:29.32,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You did a good job. Allow me to\Nexpress my gratitude by killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:30.71,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Masami{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:36.99,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:44.57,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.18,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:50.74,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the boy from the detective agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:52.31,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,How did you know I was here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:53.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,My transmitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:54.25,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Transmitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:20:00.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,When we first met at the agency,\NI accidentally stuck it on your watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:04.95,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,After following the signal, I arrived\Nat the hotel and then ran into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:07.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Seeing you with all the large suitcases,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:10.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I realized you were leaving with\Nthe billion yen that you stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:13.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:16.06,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Conan Edogawa. A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:19.77,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I had no idea there was anything on the watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:23.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But the watch belonged to that big man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:29.81,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No, he broke his own watch when he\Nlost control and killed Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:31.84,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,so I gave him mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:36.18,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,This guy intended to kill everyone\Nfrom the very start, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:37.12,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:38.65,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hirota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} realized this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,so he betrayed us before\Nwe knew what was happening
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:45.52,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that mean this man is the mastermind behind the billion-yen robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:50.40,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right. Okita scouted for people he needed to realize his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:58.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He would put these people into teams\Nand have them commit robberies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:01.61,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Rumor had it that he would eliminate\Nhis recruits to keep them silent
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:03.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,after they would finish his jobs,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:06.11,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,but I didn't know it was the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:12.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not going to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:14.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:18.96,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll tell you where the suitcases\Nwith the one billion yen are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.63,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The front desk of the hotel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,How did you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:26.77,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,When you got in the taxi,\Nyou didn't have the suitcases with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:28.10,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I simply assumed that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.54,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:31.06,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:35.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You talk too much, woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:48.65,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Masami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.65,0:21:50.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Who's he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:56.63,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The boss behind the billion yen robbery!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:06.74,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as she had said, the billion\Nyen were being kept at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:09.54,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The bill codes matched\Nthose of the stolen money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:12.74,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Thus the billion-yen robbery case came to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:23.08,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, little detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:06.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:06.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next episode's hint right after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.84,0:24:01.97,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.97,0:24:04.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The shot came from the top of the building across the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.71,0:24:10.58,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What does this coded number message say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.58,0:24:13.65,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,They could be road numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.65,0:24:16.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Like Route 162, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:18.84,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Get this helicopter moving, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.42,0:24:30.38,Signs,Comment,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.38,0:24:35.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Take a good look at a regular electronic calculator.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.36,0:24:38.70,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, we'll turn your way of looking at things upside-down!
